# No Emojis Or Decorative Icons By Default

- Do not add emojis or decorative icon glyphs in UI text, labels, titles, logs, comments, docs, or commit/PR text.
- Keep text-only wording by default.
- Only use emojis or decorative icons when the user explicitly asks for them in the current request.
- If uncertain whether an icon is desired, prefer no icon.
